(5, 6, '6', 'Learn UI/UX design at Goglow hub', '<p><strong>UI/X DESIGN</strong></p>\r\n', '<p>UI design and UX design are two of the most often confused and conflated terms in web and app design. And understandably so. They&rsquo;re usually placed together in a single term, UI/UX design, and viewed from the surface they seem to be describing the same thing. It&rsquo;s often hard to find solid descriptions of the two that don&rsquo;t descend too far into jargon. But fear not! GOGLOW HUB got you covered. We would take you through the learning process, from the basic to the expert level.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>What is UI Design?</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The &ldquo;UI&rdquo; in UI design stands for &ldquo;user interface.&rdquo; The user interface is the graphical layout of an application. It consists of the buttons users click on, the text they read, the images, sliders, text entry fields, and all the rest of the items the user interacts with. This includes screen layout, transitions, interface animations, and every single micro-interaction. Any sort of visual element, interaction, or animation must all be designed.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This job falls to UI designers and UI/UX design agencies. They decide what the application is going to look like. They have to choose color schemes and button shapes &mdash; the width of lines and the fonts used for text. UI/UX designers create the look and feel of an application&rsquo;s user interface.<img alt=\"ux tools ui vs ux\" src=\"https://www.datocms-assets.com/48294/1617110613-1uivsux.png?auto=format\" style=\"height:100%; width:100%\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>UI designers are also graphic designers. They&rsquo;re concerned with aesthetics. It&rsquo;s up to them to make sure the application&rsquo;s interface is attractive, visually stimulating, and themed appropriately to match the purpose and/or personality of the app. And they need to make sure every single visual element feels united, both aesthetically, and in purpose.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>What is UX Design?</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&ldquo;UX&rdquo; stands for &ldquo;user experience.&rdquo; A user&rsquo;s experience of the app is determined by how they interact with it. Is the experience smooth and intuitive or clunky and confusing? Does navigating the app feel logical or does it feel arbitrary? Does interacting with the app give people the sense that they&rsquo;re efficiently accomplishing the tasks they set out to achieve or does it feel like a struggle? User experience is determined by how easy or difficult it is to interact with the user interface elements that the UI designers have created.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"ui vs ux whiteboard\" src=\"https://www.datocms-assets.com/48294/1617110654-2uivsux.jpg?auto=format\" style=\"height:100%; width:100%\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>So UX designers are also concerned with an application&rsquo;s user interface, and this is why people get confused about the difference between the two. But whereas UI designers are tasked with deciding how the user interface will look, UX designers are in charge of determining how the user interface operates also known as UX strategy.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>They determine the structure of the interface and the functionality. How it&rsquo;s organized and how all the parts relate to one another. In short, they design how the interface works. If it works well and feels seamless, the user will have a good experience. But if navigation is complicated or unintuitive, then a lousy user experience is likely. UX designers work to avoid the second scenario.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>UI design and UX design involve very different skill sets, but they are integral to each other&rsquo;s success. A beautiful design can&rsquo;t save an interface that&rsquo;s clunky and confusing to navigate, and a brilliant, perfectly-appropriate user experience can be sunk by bad visual interface design that makes using the app unpleasant. Both UI and UX designs need to be flawlessly executed and perfectly aligned with pre-existing user expectations to create an excellent user interface/experience. And when those stars align the results can be astounding.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>At <strong>GOGLOW HUB</strong> we teach you how to be a guru in <strong>UIUX DESIGN.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.hub.goglowonline.com/index\">Click on the link below to enroll for your UI/UX Design</a></p>\r\n', 'Fri Apr 15 2022', 65, 'upload/ux_ui.png', 'Goglow', 'www.hub.goglowonline.com', 'Approved'),
(8, 8, '8', 'Learn Graphics Design at Goglow hub.', '<p>Learn Graphics Design</p>\r\n', '<p><strong>WHAT IS GRAPHICS DESIGN?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Graphics Design can be defined as the one of the most common tech-related courses in recent times. This is the art and profession of selecting and arranging visual elements such as topography,images,etc to convey a message to the audience/viewer.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We could also say it is a communication design. It is a way of conveying ideas through vision and displays. It is the primary duty of the graphics designer to create visual concepts that communicates ideas and inspires. This goes on to say that graphics design goes beyond the combination of colors but also the ability to interact with the viewer.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>There are 7 major types of Graphics Design. they are;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Product design.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Branding design.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Website design.</li>\r\n	<li>Print design.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Publishing design.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Environmental design.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Animation design.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>GOGLOW HUB</strong> would teach you these types and also how to be an expert designer.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.hub.goglowonline.com\">Click here to register for GRAPHICS DESIGN</a></p>\r\n', 'Wed Aug 31 2022', 66, 'upload/graphic1.jpg', 'Tech', 'www.hub.goglowonline.com', 'Approved'),
(9, 8, '8', 'Learn TOEFL & IELTS', '<p><strong>Score well in your IELTS &amp; TOEFL</strong></p>\r\n', '<p>IELTS/TOEFL is conducted for people seeking educational and job opportunities in English-speaking countries so that their ability to overcome the linguistic gap and undertake communication efficiently in a foreign country can be assessed.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://www.currentschoolnews.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/TOEFL-iBT-Vs-TOEFL-PBT.jpg\" style=\"height:200px; width:320px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>IELTS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The International English Language Testing System,(IELTS)&nbsp; which was established in 1989 is a&nbsp;standardized test of English language proficiency for non-native English language speakers.&nbsp;If you are lookling forward to migrate, as either a student or worker, to&nbsp;countries&nbsp;like ,Canada,etc then&nbsp;writing either the IELTS&nbsp;&amp; TOEFL&nbsp;is the first step to take.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>TOEFL</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The test of English as a foreign language (TOEFL)&nbsp; which is similar to IELTS&nbsp;&nbsp;is also widely accepted in over 11,000 Universities and 190 countries. It is also done to measure the English-speaking proficiency of people.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Even though,IELTS&nbsp;&nbsp;are shorter than TOEFL&nbsp;and&nbsp;generally requires that you only use either US English or UK English, they are both basic requirements for migration.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>These tests come in four different sections&nbsp;such as <strong>LISTENING, READING, WRITING &amp; SPEAKING.&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Here at <strong>GOGLOW HUB</strong>,we train you to be fully prepared to score high in these tests.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.hub.goglowonline.com\">Click here to register</a></p>\r\n', 'Wed Aug 31 2022', 51, 'upload/ielts1.jpg', 'Tech', 'www.hub.goglowonline.com', 'Approved'),
(10, 8, '8', 'Computer Appreciation', '<p>Microsoft Word,excel,powerpoint,etc</p>\r\n', '<p>In this modern world of technological development,it could be considered a downgrade to any one who is not techonolocally-inclined.&nbsp;&nbsp;This program helps in the&nbsp;&nbsp;creating, managing, processing and exchanging of information using the computer. These are the major areas/topics that give a full understanding of computer and it&#39;s basic functions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Here at&nbsp; <strong>GOGLOW HUB</strong>, we help students to understand the computer better thereby helping in thier navigations and usage.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Computer Appreciation program is a program that consist of;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>MICROSOFT EXCEL</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>MICROSOFT ACCESS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>MICROSOFT POWERPOINT</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>INTERNET AND EMAIL UTILIZATION&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>TYPING SKILL</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>MICROSOFT WORD&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Click on link below to register for this course.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'Wed Aug 31 2022', 60, 'upload/computerappreciation.jpg', 'Tech', 'www.hub.goglowonline.com', 'Approved'),
(11, 8, '8', 'Digital Video Editing', '<p>Video editing</p>\r\n', '<p>Videos are an important way to record memories, pass information. They also establish authority and a more personal feel to the information being passed. Video editing is simply the arrangement and manipulation of video shots.It can be used to structure and pass information through videos.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With the improvement in the digital world over the years, it is pertinent to say that there has been a visible development in the process of video editing. Video editing course is one of the top 20 digital skill to learn and perfect in recent times, we can also that video editing systems have become more versatile and accessible.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It is important to note too that video editing goes beyond putting together of videos in sequence and addition of background music with subtitles. Although, these tend to be the basics, there are much more to learn in this tech-related skill.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>There are two main types of Video editing. Here at GOGLOW HUB, we do not just teach you these types but we also teach when and how to be applied effectively both in the city of Owerri and beyond.&nbsp;There is also an opportunity of Internship after finishing the program.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>GOGLOW HUB gives you nothing but the best.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.hub.goglowonline.com\">Click here to register!</a></p>\r\n', 'Thu Sep 01 2022', 86, 'upload/videoediting1.jpg', 'Tech', 'www.hub.goglowonline.com', 'Approved'),
