(13, 8, '8', 'Solar Panel Installation', '<p>Solar Panel Installation</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sun Energy</p>\r\n', '<p>Solar Systems are made up of solar panels,&nbsp;a mounting system, and a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.greenmatch.co.uk/blog/2018/11/solar-pv-inverter-replacement-cost-uk\">solar inverter</a>&nbsp;with computerised controller. Solar panels produce&nbsp;<strong>DC electricity</strong>&nbsp;from&nbsp;<strong>sunlight</strong>. Then the inverter converts the generated electricity into&nbsp;<strong>AC</strong>, so that it can be used in the household. The computerised controller manages the solar system and ensures&nbsp;<strong>optimal performance</strong>. If you want battery<strong>&nbsp;backup system</strong>&nbsp;or an off-the-grid solar system, a&nbsp;<strong>battery</strong>&nbsp;is required.&nbsp;&nbsp;Solar polar&nbsp;systems derive clean, pure energy from the sun. Installing solar panels&nbsp;on your home and office spaces&nbsp;helps combat greenhouse gas emissions This is a conservative way of energy as it requires little or no assistance.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://st3.idealista.com/cms/archivos/styles/idcms_social_large_desktop/public/2020-08/media/image/panel-2562239_1280.jpg?fv=4P-MkHaX&amp;itok=zHEBIXB6\" style=\"height:390px; width:744px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>There are six major things to consider when installing solar panels. They are:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Step 1: Choose the right technology.</li>\r\n	<li>Step 2:Measure your energy use.</li>\r\n	<li>Step 3: Check your local financial incentives.</li>\r\n	<li>Step 4: Decide the correct positioning.</li>\r\n	<li>Step 5: Decide if you want a battery.</li>\r\n	<li>Step 6: Choose a good installer.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Here at Goglow Hub, we would take you through the right steps to a good solar panel installation process.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://hub,goglowonline.com\">Click to register for this course</a></p>\r\n', 'Tue Sep 06 2022', 85, 'upload/solar2.jpg', 'Tech', 'www.hub.goglowonline.com', 'Approved'),
