form.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You may also want to read&nbsp;<a href=\"https://aitechnologiesng.com/android-app-development-training-in-abuja/\">Android App Development Training a</a><a href=\"https://hub.goglowonline.com/product-detail.php?post_id=677\">t Goglow Hub</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><a href=\"https://hub.goglowonline.com/contact-us\">APPLY HERE</a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Usage of Android Studio IDE</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>In this app development training at Goglow Hub,&nbsp;we will teach you what an android studio is. We will take you through why Android Studio is Android&#39;s official IDE.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In this training course at Goglow Hub, we will train you on why It is purpose-built for Android to accelerate your development and help you build the highest-quality apps for every Android device.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In this app development training at Goglow Hub,&nbsp;we will teach you what the code editor is.&nbsp; in this computer training program, you will learn why the code editor helps you write better code.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Why it works faster and makes you more productive by offering advanced code completion, refactoring, and code analysis.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You will learn what an Android emulator is. Why it installs and starts your apps faster than a real device and allows you to prototype and test your app on various Android device configurations: phones, tablets, Android Wear, and Android TV devices.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In this App development training course at Goglow Hub, you will learn how you can simulate a variety of hardware features such as GPS location, network latency, motion sensors, and multi-touch input.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You will learn how to use Android Studio&rsquo;s extensive tools to test your Android apps with JUnit 4 and functional UI test frameworks.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We will train you on how to run your tests on a device, an emulator, a continuous integration environment, or in Firebase Test Lab.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Usage of Eclipses</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://aitechnologiesng.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/swift-300x150.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In this app development training at Goglow Hub,&nbsp;Nigeria you will learn why Eclipse is a powerful, open-source, integrated development environment (IDE) that facilitates the creation of desktop, mobile, and web applications</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You will learn how versatile and adaptable an Eclipse is in app development and why an Eclipse uses the concept of a workspace for organizing projects.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Usage and customization of list views to display data</p>\r\n\r\n<p>in this training course at Goglow Hub, you will learn why ListView is widely used in android applications to display data. We will take you through the various examples of a list view in App development.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You will learn why&nbsp;<strong>Listview</strong>&nbsp;is present inside Containers and how you can drag and drop it on a virtual mobile screen to create it.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Fundamentals of the Java programming language</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In this app development training at Goglow Hub,&nbsp;we will take you through the fundamentals of Java programming language.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In this app development course, we aim to provide beginning programmers with a basic understanding of the Java language and tools also object-oriented programming and design.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You will learn how to write simple Object-oriented programs in Java and how to run unit tests to verify program behaviour.</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><strong>Run the Android Virtual Device emulator</strong></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>In this app development training at Goglow Hub,&nbsp;you will learn what an Android virtual device emulator is. how the Android Emulator simulates Android devices on your computer so that you can test your application on a variety of devices and Android API levels without needing to have each physical device.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>in this training course at Goglow Hub, you will learn how you can simulate incoming phone calls and text messages, specify the location of the device, simulate different network speeds, simulate rotation and other hardware sensors, and access the Google Play Store, and much more.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You will learn why the emulator comes with predefined configurations for various Android phones, tablets, Wear OS, and Android TV devices.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://aitechnologiesng.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/kotlin-300x158.png\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Write true native applications in JavaScript across multiple platforms</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In this App development training course at Goglow Hub&nbsp;Nigeria, you will learn how to write true native applications in JavaScript across multiple platforms.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Introduction of the most important pieces of React Native development</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In this app development training at Goglow Hub,&nbsp;we will introduce you to the most important pieces of React Native development and how important React native is today to app development.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You will learn why React Native is a JavaScript framework for writing real, natively rendering mobile applications for iOS and Android.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You will learn why react-native targets mobile platforms. We will teach you how with React native web developers can write mobile applications that look and feel truly &ldquo;native,&rdquo; all from the comfort of a JavaScript library.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In this training course at Goglow Hub, you will learn why React Native makes it easy to simultaneously develop an App for both Android and iOS.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You will learn why react native is a multiple platform system and why google encourages developers to learn react native in addition to knowing Java.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This App development training course at Goglow Hub&nbsp;is filled with knowledge. If you want to be a developer, we encourage you to make it a resolution to learn this important course at the Goglow Hub computer training centr