side from giving you the main programming knowledge, we will take you through the steps to become a very good software developer.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>You may also want to read</strong><a href=\"https://aitechnologiesng.com/app-development-training-in-abuja/\"><strong>: </strong></a><strong><a href=\"https://hub.goglowonline.com/product-detail.php?post_id=678\">App development Training&nbsp;</a></strong><a href=\"https://hub.goglowonline.com/product-detail.php?post_id=678\">at Goglow Hub</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>why you need to be clear about what you want</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>In this Software Development Training at Goglow Hub, you will learn why you need to be clear about what you want if you want to be a good software developer.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You will learn why it is very important to set goals if you must succeed as a software developer. You need to set goals, like; I want to work as a software developer at an established tech company, I want to work at a brand new startup, as a software engineer, in the industry I adore and I want to build things on a team and get paid well for it</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>You will learn that commitment to the course of training is key no matter your end goal.</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"In this Software Development Training in Abuja\" src=\"https://aitechnologiesng.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Software-Development-Training-in-Abuja1-1024x768.jpg\" style=\"height:100%; width:100%\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>In this Software Development Training at Goglow Hub aside from teaching you software Development we guide you through the programming languages to learn.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You will learn from us that once you know a particular language, it is not difficult to transition to new ones. That means that when you&rsquo;re becoming a software developer, what you want to focus on is understanding programming fundamentals.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For you to be a very good Software Developer you need to practice a lot. In this training course, you will learn how to practice, practice and practice again.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In this Software Development Training at Goglow Hub,&nbsp;You will learn how to use tools that real software developers use. You will learn how to use tools like Github.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This will enable you to adjust much faster once you&rsquo;re in a real job, rather than having yet another steep learning curve to master.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We will teach you how to read codes written by other Software developers. You will learn how to browse through GitHub repositories and how to look through documentation.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Find a supportive software engineering community&nbsp;</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>In this software development training course at Goglow Hub, you will learn how to find supportive software Engineering Communities.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>When you are surrounded by a community of like-minded people, you have an automatic support system: a group of individuals you can call on when you get stuck, or lose motivation.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Build actual coding projects&nbsp;</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>You will learn how to solve problems just like real developers. in this training course at the Goglow Hub,&nbsp;you will learn how to build real-time coding projects.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>you&rsquo;ll have plenty of projects to show off. You&rsquo;ll build several applications throughout the course.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Other Attractions</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Aside from taking you through this Software development course, there are other attractions attached to learning with us.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We run one-on-one training. Each instructor is dedicated to a particular student. This allows the student to ask as many questions as they may wish to ask without feeling as if they are disrupting other people&#39;s learning programs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This is what our students enjoy most about learning with us.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you register for this Software development training course in Goglow Hub, you will enjoy learning with the mindset that even if you don&rsquo;t understand at the moment you can re-watch the day&rsquo;s training at your convenient time and venue.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>At Goglow Hub, We have a Unique students portal where we&nbsp;upload videos after each day&rsquo;s training section so you can re-watch them at your convenient time. It is the&nbsp;first in Nigeria.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We developed this portal to make it easy for our students to learn and know.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We train in a serene and conducive environment, which makes learning easier.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our certificate is Globally recognized.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Register with us today to learn software development at our training centre at Goglow Hub and we can guarantee you that you will have value for money.</p>\r\n', 'GOGLOW HUB', 'Approved'),
