(693, 'GOGLOW', 'upload/ielts10.png', 'upload/ielts11.jpg', 'upload/ielts5.jpg', 'IELTS Training', 'Offline', '1 Week', 'Goglow Hub Certification', 'IELTS Training + Exam Fee (1 Week)', '160000', '<ul>\r\n	<li>read, listen and then speak in response to a question</li>\r\n	<li>listen and then speak in response to a question</li>\r\n	<li>read, listen and then write in response to a question</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<h1>Prepare for IELTS</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Prepare for your test with a range of free IELTS study materials and resources from the British Council.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The first step making sure you are ready to take IELTS is to prepare for it so you know what to expect on the test day.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our IELTS learning materials will get you acquainted with the test format and also improve your confidence when writing, speaking, reading and listening in English.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Even if you believe you are a proficient user of English, we still recommend that you prepare thoroughly for your test with our helpful IELTS training resources.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>At a Glance</h2>\r\n\r\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" style=\"width:100%\" summary=\"What To Expect\">\r\n	<caption>IELTS Braekdown</caption>\r\n	<thead>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th scope=\"col\">Section</th>\r\n			<th scope=\"col\">Time Limit</th>\r\n			<th scope=\"col\">Questions</th>\r\n			<th scope=\"col\">Tasks</th>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</thead>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Reading</td>\r\n			<td>54&ndash;72 minutes</td>\r\n			<td>30&ndash;40 questions</td>\r\n			<td>Read passages and respond to questions</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Listening</td>\r\n			<td>41&ndash;57 minutes</td>\r\n			<td>28&ndash;39 questions</td>\r\n			<td>Answer questions about brief lectures or classroom discussions</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Break</td>\r\n			<td>10 minutes</td>\r\n			<td>&mdash;</td>\r\n			<td>&mdash;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Speaking</td>\r\n			<td>17 minutes</t