(703, 'GOGLOW', 'upload/DATA ANALYSIS3.jpeg', 'upload/DATA ANALYSIS1.png', 'upload/DATA ANALYSIS2.jpeg', 'Data Analytics', 'Offline', '2 Months', 'Goglow Hub Certification', 'DATA ANALYSIS (3 MONTHS)', '155000', '<p>Data Analysis in Power BI course is designed to take learners from a beginner&rsquo;s level to advanced level of using Power BI. It is designed to equip you with the essential skills needed to analyze, visualize, and present data effectively using Microsoft Power BI. &nbsp;At the end of this course, learners would learn how to confidently use Power BI for data analysis tasks.</p>\r\n', '<p>Whether you&#39;re a beginner looking to establish a solid foundation or an experienced user aiming to enhance your existing knowledge, this course is tailored to meet your needs. Throughout this training, you will dive deep into the world of Excel and explore a wide range of topics. By the end of the course, you can expect to:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; &nbsp;Develop a strong foundation: Master the basics of Excel, including navigating the interface, working with worksheets, and managing data effectively.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; &nbsp;Efficient data entry and manipulation: Learn powerful techniques to input, format, and organize data efficiently. Explore functions, formulas, and shortcuts to streamline your data entry process.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; &nbsp;Advanced data analysis: Unleash the power of Excel&#39;s data analysis tools, including sorting, filtering, and pivot tables. Dive into statistical functions, what-if analysis, and data visualization techniques.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; &nbsp;Visualizing data with charts and graphs: Master the art of creating impactful visualizations to effectively communicate your data. Explore different chart types, customize their appearance, and present your insights in a visually appealing manner.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; &nbsp;Collaborative work and data sharing: Explore techniques for collaborating on Excel workbooks with others, sharing data securely, and protecting sensitive information. Learn to track changes, consolidate data, and work seamlessly with multiple users. Projects, Projects, Projects Data Analysis in Power BI course is designed to take learners from a beginner&rsquo;s level to advanced level of using Power BI. It is designed to equip you with the essential skills needed to analyze, visualize, and present data effectively using Microsoft Power BI. &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>At the end of this course, learners would learn how to confidently use Power BI for data analysis tasks.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; &nbsp;Introduction to Power BI: Get acquainted with the Power BI ecosystem, understand its components, and learn to navigate the Power BI interface.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; &nbsp;Connecting to Data Sources: Learn how to connect to various data sources, including Excel, databases, cloud services, and online platforms. Master data transformation techniques to clean, shape, and model your data.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; &nbsp;Creating Visualizations: Dive into the world of data visualization and discover the rich library of visual elements offered by Power BI. Learn to create compelling charts, graphs, tables, maps, and interactive dashboards to present your insights effectively. &bull; &nbsp;Advanced Data Modeling: Explore advanced data modeling techniques in Power BI, such as creating relationships between tables, defining calculated columns and measures, and working with complex data hierarchies.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; &nbsp;DAX (Data Analysis Expressions): Develop expertise in the DAX language, Power BI&#39;s formula language, to perform powerful calculations, create custom measures, and derive insights from your data.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; &nbsp;Interactive Reporting and Dashboards: Learn how to build interactive reports and dynamic dashboards that provide actionable insights. Master the art of creating drill-through and cross-filtering experiences for enhanced data exploration. Power BI Service: Get hands-on experience with the Power BI service, the cloud-based platform for publishing, sharing, and collaborating on Power BI content. Learn how to create workspaces, set up security permissions, and distribute your reports and dashboards.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Fundamentals of SQL Learners are taught the fundamentals of SQL by being exposed to the terminologies and different concepts that are available in SQL. Learners will understand how to query data stored in a relational database.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; &nbsp;Introduction to Databases: Understand the fundamentals of relational databases, learn about different database management systems (DBMS), and explore SQL&#39;s role in managing data.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; &nbsp;SQL Basics: Get started with SQL by learning the syntax, keywords, and common data types. Learn to write basic SQL queries to retrieve, insert, update, and delete data from databases.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; &nbsp;Database Modeling: Learn how to create tables, define relationships between them, and ensure data integrity.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; &nbsp;Advanced SQL Queries: Take your SQL skills to the next level by mastering complex querying techniques. Explore subqueries, joins, set operations, and conditional logic to retrieve and analyze data from multiple tables. Data Aggregation and Reporting: Explore advanced SQL functions to aggregate and summarize data. Master techniques to calculate totals, averages, and perform grouping and sorting for insightful reporting.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Don&#39;t miss this opportunity to master the skills needed to thrive as a data analyst. Enroll in our Bootcamp Course today and gain the skills you need to become a proficient professional!</p>\r\n', 'GOGLOW HUB', 'Approved'),
(704, 'GOGLOW', 'upload/goglow-cctv1.jpeg', 'upload/goglow-cctv2.jpeg', 'upload/goglow-cctv3.jpeg', 'CCTV Installation', 'Offline', '1 Month', 'Goglow Hub Certification', 'CCTV Installation - - Security CCTV Engineer (1 Month)', '25000', '<p>CCTV (<strong>closed-circuit television</strong>) is a TV system in which signals are not publicly distributed but are monitored, primarily for surveillance and security purposes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Learn&nbsp;CCTV Security Systems From Pro: IP CCTV, HD CCTV &amp; Analogue, Made in Nigeria&nbsp;for: Beginners &amp; Professionals</p>\r\n', '<h2>What you&#39;ll learn</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Skills that will help you enter booming security industry and get well paid job. Security is rapidly shifting from old CCTV and Alarm Systems to IP systems.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Setup of DVRs with HD cameras, use of 2MP, 3MP, 5MP or 8MP (4K - Ultra HD) cameras, HD camera formats: TVI, CVI, AHD, SDI.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Programming of IP cameras and NVRs with live examples. IP camera and NVR types and difference between them.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Video compression, comparison of H.264, H.265, H.265+, what frames per second (fps) to pick.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Basics of IP Networks required to work with IP Camera Systems: Ethernet connections, IP addresses, ports, routers and switches.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Tools and software required to work with IP cameras. Live examples how to use the software.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>How CCTV camera works, how to calculate focal length required for your surveillance objective, camera parameters.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 'GOGLOW HUB', 'Approved'),
(705, 'GOGLOW', 'upload/goglow-solar1.jpg', 'upload/goglow-solar3.jpg', 'upload/goglow-solar2.webp', 'Solar Panel Installation', 'Offline', '1 Month', 'Goglow Hub Certification', 'Solar Panel Installation', '25000', '<p>The only online course with everything you need to know on Solar Energy - 2023.&nbsp;There are many reasons why you should learn solar panel installation. One of the most important reasons is that it provides a clean and green source of energy and produces no greenhouse gases or carbon emissions.&nbsp;An average-size home with a solar panel installation will save over one tonne of carbon dioxide from entering the atmosphere every year</p>\r\n', '<h2>What you&#39;ll learn</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Design your own Grid-Tie PV System</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Learn everything on Solar Modules, Optimizers (DC/DC converters), Junction Boxes, Inverterers, Solar Meters</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Calculate Solar Array size</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Determine and select the correct components for the Solar PV system</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Calculate Peak Sun Hours for any location in the world!</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Determine if the Roof Pitch and Azimuth of a property is good for a Solar System</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Determine the optimum panel placement for Solar PV</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Calculate efficiency losses due to Roof Pitch/Azimuth and equipments</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Energy production curve of a PV system vs. house energy needs</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Learn about the Solar Cells Chemistry</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Learn about Monocrystalline vs. Polycrystalline modules</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Learn the wiring foundations</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Build your own Grid-Tie Solar design</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Power concepts &amp; Units</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Learn all the fundamentals of Solar PV energy</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Applications of Solar PV Systems</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Foundations about Off-Grid vs. Grid-Tie</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>How does a PV system work</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Learn in detail about the components of a typical PV system</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Advantages and Disadvantages of Solar photovoltaic energy</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 'GOGLOW HUB', 'Approved');
